{{Quote|Because one Zeltron is irresistibles, and ten Zeltrons are forces of natures! Or to puts it anothers way, one splash of this and you'll smells better to the ladies.|[[Jojo (holodrama character)|Jojo]]|<ref name="Zeltros: Pleasure Planet">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20040105zeltros|text=Zeltros: Pleasure Planet|int=Zeltros: Pleasure Planet}}</ref>}}
'''Essence of Zeltros''' was a [[Color/Legends|blue]] [[Perfume/Legends|perfume]] that was produced by the government of [[Zeltros/Legends|Zeltros]] and highlighted on the popular [[Holodrama/Legends|holodrama]] ''[[Zeltrons in Love]]''. Produced from actual [[Zeltron/Legends|Zeltron]] [[Pheromone/Legends|pheromones]], one spritz of the perfume gave the user one [[Standard hour/Legends|hour]] of the Zeltrons' famous seductive abilities, or magnified the effects of a Zeltron's own pheromones. One bottle held twenty applications, weighed .1 [[Kilogram/Legends|kilograms]], and cost one hundred [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]].

